high_descs: Turn back and enter into the room and turn right and move towards the desk.
Take a grape bunch which is placed next to the laptop.
Turn your right and come out of the room, again turn right and enter into the kitchen, then head towards the sink.
Put the grape bunch next to the sink.
Turn your right and walk out of the kitchen and enter into the bedroo
Take another grape bunch from the bed.
Come out of the bedroom and again enter into the kitchen and turn right to reach the sink.
Place the second grape next to the first grape in the sink.
anns.task_desc: Place the bunch of grapes on the top of the sink

high_descs: Turn right to enter the room on the right and reach the table next to the desk.
Pick up the grape from the table.
Turn around to exit the room and turn right to enter the kitchen and reach the sink on the right.
Put the grape on the left sink.
Turn right to exit the kitchen and turn right to reach the bed.
Pick up the grape from the pot.
Turn around to exit the bedroom and turn left to enter the kitchen and hang right to reach the sink.
Put the grape on the left sink.
anns.task_desc: Put two bunches of grapes on the left sink.

high_descs: Turn right and enter the door ahead to the room with two desks.
Pick up the bunch of grape on the desk next to the laptop.
Exit the room the way you came in, then turn right and right again towards the kitchen sink.
Place the grape on the counter to the left of the sink.
Turn right, go straight to the wall between the two doorways, and enter the doorway on the right, going straight to the bed.
Pick up the grape on the bed.
Return to the sink where you placed the first bunch of grapes down.
Place the grape down next to the first bunch of grapes on the sink.
anns.task_desc: Place two bunches of Grape down on a Sink.
